title: What was Tiny Tim famous for besides Tip-toe Through the Tulips'? - Quora

response.answer_text: Getting married on the Tonight Show and being the most obnoxious untalented wack job ever to be the music business.
He did a lot of covers. Always passionate. "Livin' in the Sunlight, Lovin' in the Moonlight" and “Over The Rainbow”. These two by him were fairly popular.
